<center><H1>VPN White Papers</H1></center>

<p>
VPNC's members often create reports and white papers on
various topics that relate to VPN technologies. This page
lists papers on many current topics in the VPN market.
Of course, because the papers are written by the
individual companies, it is likely that each will have
a slant towards the views and markets of the companies
that write the papers.

<p>VPNC has its own
<a href="vpn-technologies.html">white paper on VPN technologies</a>
that defines VPNs.


<p><hr align=center width="90%"><p>
<h2>VPN Overviews</h2>

<p><a href="http://www.cisco.com/en/US/solutions/collateral/ns340/ns394/ns171/ns461/net_brochure09186a00800b0da5.html">
Voice and Video Enabled IPSec VPN Solution Overview</a>, from Cisco

<p><a href="http://www.ciscopress.com/content/images/1587051796/samplechapter/1587051796content.pdf">
What Is a Virtual Private Network?</a>, from Cisco (which is an excerpt from
<a href="http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/1587051796">this book</a>)

<p><a href="http://www.cyberoam.com/cyberoam/jsp/resources/resources.jsp?tab=0">
Threat Free Tunneling : Securing the VPN Traffic</a>, from Cyberoam

<p><hr align=center width="90%"><p>
<h2>VPN Technologies and Cryptography</h2>

<p><a href="http://www.cisco.com/en/US/netsol/ns465/networking_solutions_white_paper0900aecd801b1b0f.shtml">
Managed VPN - Comparison of MPLS, IPSec, and SSL Architectures</a>
from Cisco

<p><a href="http://tools.netgear.com/media/whitepapers/VPN_Security.pdf">
Security & Savings with Virtual Private Networks</a>,
from NETGEAR

<p><a href="http://www.ciscopress.com/articles/article.asp?p=1218144">
SSL VPN Design Considerations</a>, from Cisco


<p><hr align=center width="90%"><p>
<h2>Business Case for VPNs</h2>

<p><a href="http://authentec.com/Portals/5/Documents/Smart_Grid%28web%29.pdf">
Securing the Smart Grid</a>
from INSIDE Secure


<p><hr align=center width="90%"><p>
<h2>VPNs and Remote Access</h2>

<p><a href='http://www.cisco.com/en/US/prod/collateral/vpndevc/ps6032/ps6094/ps6120/prod_white_paper0900aecd804fb79a.html'>
Remote-Access VPNs: Business Productivity, Deployment, and Security Considerations</a>, from Cisco

